  "original_title": "\u0b87\u0bb2\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8 \u0ba4\u0bae\u0bbf\u0bb4\u0bb0\u0b9a\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd \u0b95\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bbf \u0b85\u0bb2\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bb2\u0b95\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1 \u0b9c\u0bc2\u0bb2\u0bc8 \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bc8\u0bb5\u0bc7\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b85\u0ba9\u0bc1\u0bb7\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Black July Commemoration at the Sri Lanka Tamil Rashuk Party Office",
      "author": "Digital Desk 5",
      "body_lines": [
        "A memorial was held in Jaffna to remember those killed in the 1983 Black July riots.",
        "The commemoration was held at the office of Sri Lanka Tamil Republic Party in Vadamaratsi (23) on Saturday at 10.30 am.",
        "Member of Parliament M.A. Sumanthran North Provincial Assembly, S. Sukirthan, K. Sayanthan, members of Sri Lankan Tamil Republic Party's local government councilors, members and members of the party also participated in the commemoration.",
        "During the Black July riots of 23 July 1983, many Tamils \u200b\u200bwere killed and property destroyed."
      ],
